# Analysis of the Main Target Image

## Count & Layers
The structure consists of 10 building blocks arranged in multiple components:
- A tall tower made of orange cylindrical blocks
- A red house-like structure with a yellow support beam attached to the tower
- A separate red arch structure with orange triangular roof pieces

The structure has 3 main layers vertically:
1. Base layer: Two vertical orange cylinders and the separate red arch
2. Middle layer: Yellow beam, red house with yellow half-cylinder
3. Top layer: Orange triangular pieces forming roofs and tower top

## Spatial Relationships
- Two orange vertical cylinders form the main tower
- A yellow horizontal beam extends from the middle of the tower
- A red arch structure sits on top of the yellow beam
- A yellow half-cylinder is placed inside the arch
- Orange triangular pieces form roofs on both structures
- A separate red arch structure with orange triangular roof pieces sits on the ground

# Selected Blocks from Dictionary

Based on careful analysis, the following blocks are required:
- Block #2: Red arch piece (used twice - once for the tower attachment and once for the separate structure)
- Block #8: Yellow horizontal beam
- Block #9: Orange vertical cylinder (used twice)
- Block #11: Yellow half-cylinder
- Block #15: Orange triangular piece (used three times - one for tower top and two for roofs)

# Assembly Order

```
{
    Step1: Move block with index 9 (first orange vertical cylinder)
    Step2: Move block with index 9 (second orange vertical cylinder, stacked on first)
    Step3: Move block with index 8 (yellow horizontal beam attached to cylinders)
    Step4: Move block with index 2 (red arch on yellow beam)
    Step5: Move block with index 11 (yellow half-cylinder inside arch)
    Step6: Move block with index 15 (orange triangular roof for attached structure)
    Step7: Move block with index 15 (orange triangular top for tower)
    Step8: Move block with index 2 (separate red arch structure)
    Step9: Move block with index 15 (first orange triangular roof piece for separate structure)
    Step10: Move block with index 15 (second orange triangular roof piece for separate structure)
}
```
